title: Portugal 30 Year bond-Yield
description: Portugal 30 Year Bond Yield was 3.75 percent on Tuesday November 8, according to over-the-counter interbank yield quotes for this government bond maturity. Historically, the Portugal 30 Year bond-Yield reached an all time high of 12.85 in January of 2012. This page includes a chart with historical data for Portugal 30Y.
